[MAC/LINUX] Make sure to have the following software installed and updated:
 - JAGS
 - Boost
 
Excute the following terminal commands:

CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH=/usr/include/JAGS
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH
make
sudo make install


[WINDOWS] See [1] for additional required steps (it is more straightforward to 
consider running a virtual machine running Linux)

[1] Wabersich, D., & Vandekerckhove, J. (2014). Extending JAGS: A tutorial on
    adding custom distributions to JAGS (with a diffusion model example). 
    Behavior Research Methods, 46(1), 15-28.
